Class BaseTBaseLine

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.torque.om.BaseObject
      • com.aurel.track.persist.TpBaseObject
        • com.aurel.track.persist.BaseTBaseLine
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, org.apache.torque.om.Persistent
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TBaseLine

    public abstract class BaseTBaseLine
extends TpBaseObject
    For each workitem this table contains the history of start and due dates. You should not use this class directly. It should not even be extended all references should be to TBaseLine

        public TBaseLinePeer getPeer()
        returns a peer instance associated with this om. Since Peer classes are not to have any instance attributes, this method returns the same instance for all member of this class. The method could therefore be static, but this would prevent one from overriding the behavior.
